title: Intervention S01E05 - Sara
description:
Watch Sara "The Young Mother/The Meth Addict" confront her demons in her struggle to regain custody of her child and control of her life. This episode is particularly notable for the blowup that Candy Finnegan has during the Intervention. This episode is worth watching JUST for that scene. But you hope the best for Sara. Even though zip-snow-surfing looks like fun.
Intervention, season 1, episode 5.
